belongs_to_collection.name: The Story of the Expedition Woman

overview: So-yeon is on a weekend date with her boyfriend, Ji-seok, and then she invites him to her house to save money on the motel. Her step brother, Sang-woo, comes home earlier than expected and sees them having sex. He records them secretly and plans to blackbail So-yeon with it.
title: The Story of the Expedition Woman
